---
const highlights = [
  "Diversified Holding Company Structure",
  "Multi-Sector Industrial Operations",
  "Strategic Investments & Growth Management",
  "Strong Corporate Governance Framework",
  "Sustainable and Long-Term Business Model"
];

const stats = [
  { label: "Years of Industry Experience", value: "10+" },
  { label: "Subsidiary Companies", value: "Multiple" },
  { label: "Operations", value: "Nationwide" },
  { label: "Portfolio", value: "Cross-Industry" }
];
---

<section id="about" class="section-padding container-custom overflow-hidden">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">
    
    <!-- Left: Large Industrial Image with Floating Card -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-5 order-2 lg:order-1 relative" data-reveal>
      <div class="container-rounded aspect-[4/5] shadow-2xl relative z-10 overflow-hidden group">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581091226825-a6a2a5aee158?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1000" 
          alt="Bin Naeem Industries Industrial Excellence" 
          class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[20%] group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-1000"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#111827]/60 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Decorative Element -->
      <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 w-48 h-48 bg-[#111827]/5 rounded-full -z-10 animate-float"></div>
      <div class="absolute -top-12 -right-12 w-64 h-64 border border-[#111827]/10 rounded-full -z-10"></div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Right: Content & Copy -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-7 order-1 lg:order-2 space-y-10" data-reveal>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#111827]/5 text-[10px] font-black tracking-widest text-[#111827] uppercase">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#111827] animate-pulse"></span>
          ABOUT BIN NAEEM INDUSTRIES
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-[1.1] text-[#111827] tracking-tighter">
          Driving Industrial Growth Through <span class="text-white bg-[#111827] px-3 py-1 rounded-sm rotate-1 inline-block mt-1">Strategic Leadership</span> and Diversified Excellence
        </h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-6 text-base lg:text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-light">
        <p>
          Bin Naeem Industries (Pvt.) Ltd. is a leading diversified holding company operating across multiple high-impact industries in Pakistan. Built on a foundation of integrity, operational excellence, and long-term strategic vision, the group oversees a portfolio of dynamic companies serving manufacturing, logistics, infrastructure, and essential industrial sectors.
        </p>
        <p>
          As a multi-industry corporate group, Bin Naeem Industries plays a critical role in strengthening supply chains, supporting infrastructure development, and advancing industrial innovation. Each subsidiary under the group operates with specialized expertise while aligning with the parent company’s unified mission.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Highlight Cards -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        {highlights.map((item) => (
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#111827]/20 transition-all group">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-[#111827]/10 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5 group-hover:bg-[#111827] transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-[#111827] group-hover:text-white"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-700">{item}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <p class="text-[15px] italic text-[#111827]/70 font-medium">
        With a commitment to innovation, operational discipline, and sustainable development, Bin Naeem Industries is shaping the future of Pakistan’s industrial landscape.
      </p>
      
      <div class="pt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-6">
        <a href="#companies" class="btn-primary w-full sm:w-auto shadow-xl">
          Explore Our Companies
        </a>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 py-2 border-l border-gray-200 pl-6">
          <div class="flex -space-x-3">
             {[1,2,3].map(() => (
               <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-white bg-gray-200 overflow-hidden ring-1 ring-gray-100">
                 <div class="w-full h-full bg-[#111827]/10"></div>
               </div>
             ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest leading-none">
            Trusted by <br /><span class="text-gray-900">Global Partners</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Animated Stats Row -->
  <div class="mt-32 grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 border-t border-gray-100 pt-16" data-reveal>
    {stats.map((stat) => (
      <div class="space-y-2 group">
        <p class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-[#111827] tracking-tighter group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">
          {stat.value}
        </p>
        <p class="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] leading-tight max-w-[120px]">
          {stat.label}
        </p>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>
